                    <p>I earned my Ph.D. in Communication Studies in 2021, building upon my M.Sc. in Communication Development (2013) and B.A. (Ed) in English Studies (2008). This unique journey provides me with a comprehensive understanding of both university administration and academic pursuits.</p>
